萬元以下罰金；致重傷者，\r\n處3年以上10年以下有期徒刑，得併科2百萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c527%2c20220608%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,交簡,527,20220608,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"527","JDATE":"20220608","JTITLE":"公共危險"}